dict.string: on alfred_script(q) tell application "Things3" show list "Today" activate end tell end alfred_script
on alfred_script(q) tell application "TaskPaper" open q activate end tell end alfred_script

on run argv set bundleID to (system attribute "alfred_workflow_bundleid")
tell application "Alfred 3" set configuration "task" to value (system attribute "task") in workflow bundleID without exportable set configuration "task_source" to value (system attribute "task_source") in workflow bundleID without exportable end tell end run

on run argv set bundleID to (system attribute "alfred_workflow_bundleid")
tell application "Alfred 3" set configuration "last_task" to value (system attribute "task") in workflow bundleID without exportable set configuration "last_task_source" to value (system attribute "task_source") in workflow bundleID without exportable end tell end run
How long to you plan to work?
🏝 It's time to take a rest!

on run argv set bundleID to (system attribute "alfred_workflow_bundleid")
tell application "Alfred 3" remove configuration "task" in workflow bundleID remove configuration "task_source" in workflow bundleID end tell end run
Persist task as a previous task
